acl: set: Usage: _build/macosx64/bin/infinit-acl --set --path PATHS [--user USERS] [OPTIONS...]

Set ACL:

Set options:
  -p [ --path ] arg         Paths
  -u [ --user ] arg         Users and groups (prefix: @<group>)
  -g [ --group ] arg        Groups
  -m [ --mode ] arg         Access mode: r,w,rw,none
  -o [ --others-mode ] arg  Access mode for other network users: r,w,rw,none
  -i [ --enable-inherit ]   New files/folders inherit from their parent 
                            directory
  --disable-inherit         New files/folders do not inherit from their parent 
                            directory
  -R [ --recursive ]        Apply recursively
  --traverse                Add read permissions to parent directories
  --verbose                 Verbose output
  --fetch                   Fetch users from the Hub if needed

Hidden options:
  --fallback-xattrs         Fallback to alternate xattr mode if system xattrs 
                            are not suppported


